      "id": 1,
      "text": "The Totoket Historical Society, founded in 1979, dedicates itself to preserving Northford’s local heritage.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        1
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://museumsdatabase.com/museums/view/5480"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "Its museum and research library hold more than 10,000 books, manuscripts, photographs, maps, and artifacts about the area.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        4
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://museumsdatabase.com/museums/view/5480"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The society works with local and state authorities to protect historic buildings from demolition or alteration.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        2
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://museumsdatabase.com/museums/view/5480"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Visitors can join guided walking tours, lectures, and workshops that explore Northford’s past.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        17
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://museumsdatabase.com/museums/view/5480"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Each year it hosts an Annual History Fair and a Spring Heritage Day celebration to showcase regional stories.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        18
