      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://museumsdatabase.com/museums/view/5480"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "text": "As a nonprofit, the Totoket Historical Society focuses on preserving the history and culture of the Totoket region for future generations.",
